summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Yesler-Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project (No. Wash. R-5); authorizing acquisition of property and property rights in Blocks 1, 4, 6, 7, 8 and 14 of Jackson St. Addition to the City of Seattle, Blocks 16 and 22 of H. L. Yesler's 1st Addition to the City of Seattle, Blocks 3, 6, 7, 10, 21, 22 and 24 of Hill Tract Addition to the City of Seattle, Block 2 of Burke's Second Addition to the City of Seattle, and Blocks 6 and 7 of Rainier Addition to the City of Seattle.
